4379 /******************************************************************/
4380 /* */
4381 /* */
4382 /******************************************************************/
4383 
4384 void Manager::DropPlayer( PlayerInfo* info, DropReason reason )
4385 {
4386 
4387  char player_name[vMAX_PLAYER_NAME_LEN + 1];
4388 
4389  PlayerInfo* player;
4390  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
4391  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
4392 
4393  Dbg_Assert( info );
4394  Dbg_Message( "Removing player %s from the game\n", info->m_Name );
4395 
4396  strcpy( player_name, info->m_Name );
4397 
4398  if( !info->IsObserving())
4399  {
4400  // if we're playing a game of graffiti, then free up all of the trick objects accumulated by the dropped client
4401  if ( skate_mod->GetGameMode()->IsTrue( "should_modulate_color" ) )
4402  {
4403  skate_mod->GetTrickObjectManager()->FreeTrickObjects( info->m_Skater->GetID() );
4404  }
4405  }
4406 
4407  if( OnServer())
4408  {
4409  if( !info->IsObserving())
4410  {
4411  // Inform all others of the quitter's departure
4412  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player;
4413  player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
4414  {
4415  if( !player->IsLocalPlayer())
4416  {
4417  MsgPlayerQuit msg;
4418  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
4419 
4420  msg.m_ObjId = info->m_Skater->GetID();
4421  msg.m_Reason = (char) reason;
4422 
4423  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
4424  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgPlayerQuit );
4425  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_PLAYER_QUIT;
4426  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
4427  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
4428  m_server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
4429  }
4430  }
4431 
4432 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
4433  if( ( reason == vREASON_QUIT ) ||
4434  ( reason == vREASON_TIMEOUT ) ||
4435  ( reason == vREASON_BAD_CONNECTION ))
4436  {
4437  if( mpStatsMan->IsLoggedIn())
4438  {
4439  mpStatsMan->PlayerLeft( info->m_Skater->GetID());
4440  }
4441  }
4442 #endif
4443  }
4444 
4445  if( ( reason == vREASON_BANNED ) ||
4446  ( reason == vREASON_KICKED ))
4447  {
4448  m_server->SendMessageTo( MSG_ID_KICKED, 0, NULL,
4449  info->m_Conn->GetIP(), info->m_Conn->GetPort(), 0 );
4450  if( reason == vREASON_BANNED )
4451  {
4452  m_server->BanConnection( info->m_Conn );
4453  }
4454 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
4455  //m_server->WaitForAsyncCallsToFinish();
4456 #endif // __PLAT_NGPS__
4457 
4458  }
4459  else if( reason == vREASON_LEFT_OUT )
4460  {
4461  m_server->SendMessageTo( MSG_ID_LEFT_OUT, 0, NULL,
4462  info->m_Conn->GetIP(), info->m_Conn->GetPort(), 0 );
4463 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
4464  //m_server->WaitForAsyncCallsToFinish();
4465 #endif // __PLAT_NGPS__
4466  }
4467  if( reason != vREASON_OBSERVING )
4468  {
4469  if( info->m_Conn )
4470  {
4471  info->m_Conn->Invalidate();
4472  //Dbg_Printf( "DestroyingAllMessageData 1\n" );
4473  info->m_Conn->DestroyAllMessageData();
4474  }
4475  }
4476 
4477  uint32 reason_checksum;
4478 
4479  switch( reason )
4480  {
4481  case vREASON_QUIT:
4482  {
4483  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_quit");
4484  break;
4485  }
4486  case vREASON_TIMEOUT:
4487  {
4488  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_timed_out");
4489  break;
4490  }
4491  case vREASON_OBSERVING:
4492  {
4493  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_now_observing");
4494  break;
4495  }
4496  case vREASON_BANNED:
4497  {
4498  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_banned");
4499  break;
4500  }
4501  case vREASON_KICKED:
4502  {
4503  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_kicked");
4504  break;
4505  }
4506  case vREASON_LEFT_OUT:
4507  {
4508  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_left_out");
4509  break;
4510  }
4511  case vREASON_BAD_CONNECTION:
4512  {
4513  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_dropped");
4514  break;
4515  }
4516  default:
4517  reason_checksum = Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_player_timed_out");
4518  break;
4519  }
4520 
4521  // If the info is about the server player, no need to print a panel message.
4522  // Currently this would only happen if the server decided to sit out
4523  if( info->IsLocalPlayer() == false )
4524  {
4525  CreateNetPanelMessage( true, reason_checksum, player_name );
4526  }
4527  if( reason == vREASON_OBSERVING )
4528  {
4529  if( info->IsKing())
4530  {
4531  if( m_crown )
4532  {
4533  m_crown->RemoveFromKing();
4534  }
4535  info->MarkAsKing( false );
4536  }
4537  if( info->HasCTFFlag())
4538  {
4539  char team_str[64];
4540  int team;
4541  Script::CStruct* pParams;
4542  PlayerInfo* local_player;
4543 
4544  team = info->HasWhichFlag();
4545  sprintf( team_str, "team_%d_name", team + 1 );
4546  pParams = new Script::CStruct;
4547 
4548  pParams->AddInteger( "team", team );
4549  pParams->AddComponent( Script::GenerateCRC("String0"), ESYMBOLTYPE_STRING, Script::GetString( team_str ));
4550  Script::RunScript( "flag_returned", pParams );
4551 
4552  delete pParams;
4553 
4554  local_player = GetLocalPlayer();
4555  if( local_player && !local_player->IsObserving())
4556  {
4557  if( local_player->m_Team == team )
4558  {
4559  Script::RunScript( "hide_ctf_arrow" );
4560  }
4561  }
4562  info->ClearCTFState();
4563  }
4564  }
4565  else
4566  {
4567  bool is_server_player;
4568 
4569  is_server_player = info->IsServerPlayer();
4570 
4571  Dbg_Printf( "Destroying Player %s\n", info->m_Name );
4572  DestroyPlayer( info );
4573  if( is_server_player )
4574  {
4575  ChooseNewServerPlayer();
4576  if( GetServerPlayer() == NULL )
4577  {
4578  if( ( skate_mod->GetGameMode()->GetNameChecksum() != Script::GenerateCRC( "netlobby" )))
4579  {
4580  Script::RunScript( "network_end_game_selected" );
4581  }
4582  }
4583  }
4584  }
4585 
4586  // Now see if the leaving of this player satisfies ending conditions
4587  bool all_done = true;
4588  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh ); player;
4589  player = NextPlayerInfo( sh ))
4590  {
4591  if( !player->m_flags.TestMask( PlayerInfo::mRUN_ENDED))
4592  {
4593  all_done = false;
4594  break;
4595  }
4596  }
4597 
4598  if( all_done )
4599  {
4600  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
4601 
4602  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_GAME_OVER;
4603  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
4604  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
4605  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player;
4606  player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
4607  {
4608  m_server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
4609  }
4610  }
4611  }
4612  else
4613  {
4614  DestroyPlayer( info );
4615  }
4616 }

4643 const char* Manager::GetNameFromArrayEntry( char* array_name, uint32 checksum )
4644 {

4646  const char* string = NULL;
4647  int i;
4648 
4649  pArray = Script::GetArray( array_name );
4650  Dbg_Assert( pArray );
4651 
4652  for( i = 0; i < (int)pArray->GetSize(); i++ )
4653  {
4654  uint32 value;
4655  Script::CStruct* pStructure;
4656 
4657 
4658  pStructure = pArray->GetStructure( i );
4659  Dbg_Assert( pStructure );
4660 
4661  pStructure->GetChecksum( "checksum", &value, true );
4662  if( value == checksum )
4663  {
4664  pStructure->GetText( "name", &string, true );
4665  }
4666  }
4667

4669 }

4722  for( i = 0; i < vMAX_MASTER_SERVERS; i++ )

4725  }
4726

4728

4730  Dbg_Assert( pArray );
4731

4733  pStructure->GetChecksum( "Checksum", &checksum, true );
4734  if( checksum == Script::GenerateCRC( "boolean_true" ))
4735  {

4737  {

4752  // 0.0.0.0

4773  Dbg_Assert( pStructure );

4802  viewer_ip = NULL;

4984 /******************************************************************/

4986 /* */
4987 /******************************************************************/
4988 
4989 void Manager::RandomizeSkaterStartingPoints( void )
4990 {
4991  int i, j, offset, max_skaters;
4992 
4993  // choose a random offset for these starting points
4994  offset = Mth::Rnd( 256 );
4995 
4996  if( InNetGame())
4997  {
4998  max_skaters = Mdl::Skate::vMAX_SKATERS;
4999  }
5000  else
5001  {
5002  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
5003  max_skaters = skate_mod->GetGameMode()->GetMaximumNumberOfPlayers();
5004 
5005  // PATCH (Mick)
5006  // If playing a splitscreen game in the park editor
5007  // then set the Maximum number of players to 2
5008  // so we only use the 1P and 2P start points
5009  // oterwise, we will use all the auto-horse points
5010  // which end up in stupid positions
5011  if (Ed::CParkEditor::Instance()->UsingCustomPark() && !skate_mod->GetGameMode()->IsTrue("is_horse")) // is it a custom park and not horse mode?
5012  {
5013  max_skaters = 2;
5014  offset = 0; // reset the offset, so they always get used the same way
5015  }
5016 
5017 
5018  }
5019 
5020  for( i = 0; i < max_skaters; i++ )
5021  {
5022  m_skater_starting_points[i] = -1;
5023  }
5024 
5025  // For each skater, choose a random starting point
5026  for( i = 0; i < max_skaters; i++ )
5027  {
5028  bool unique;
5029 
5030  // Choose a random starting point until it's unique
5031  do
5032  {
5033  m_skater_starting_points[i] = Mth::Rnd( max_skaters );
5034  unique = true;
5035  for( j = 0; j < max_skaters; j++ )
5036  {
5037  // skip myself
5038  if( i == j )
5039  {
5040  continue;
5041  }
5042 
5043  if( m_skater_starting_points[i] == m_skater_starting_points[j] )
5044  {
5045  unique = false;
5046  break;
5047  }
5048  }
5049  } while( !unique );
5050  }
5051 
5052  // Offset these random sequential numbers by a random number so that we pick
5053  // four sequential numbers within a possibly larger range of starting points
5054  for( i = 0; i < max_skaters; i++ )
5055  {
5056  m_skater_starting_points[i] += offset;
5057  }
5058 
5059  m_crown_spawn_point = Mth::Rnd( vNUM_CROWN_SPAWN_POINTS );
5060 }
5061

5063 /* */
5064 /* */

5066 
5067 void Manager::SetSkaterStartingPoints( int* start_points )
5068 {
5069  int i;
5070 
5071  for( i = 0; i < Mdl::Skate::vMAX_SKATERS; i++ )
5072  {
5073  m_skater_starting_points[i] = start_points[i];
5074  }
5075 }

5080 /******************************************************************/
5081 
5082 int Manager::GetSkaterStartingPoint( int skater_id )

5087 /******************************************************************/
5088 /* */
5089 /* */
5090 /******************************************************************/
5091 
5092 void Manager::LoadPendingPlayers( void )
5093 {
5094  PlayerInfo* player, *next;
5095  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
5096  int num_new_players;
5097 
5098  Dbg_Assert( m_server );
5099 
5100  num_new_players = 0;
5101 
5102 #ifdef __PLAT_XBOX__
5103  // Since XBOX has a quicker timeout, we need to tell clients that this process (loading pending players) may take much longer
5104  // than the timeout allows. Clients will allow the server N seconds to get back to them after receiving this message.
5105  // NOTE: This will only be guaranteed to work in LAN mode, because if the packet is lost, the original timeout will stand
5106  bool players_pending;
5107 
5108  players_pending = false;
5109  // Add all pending players to the game
5110  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5111  {
5112  if( player->IsPendingPlayer())
5113  {
5114  players_pending = true;
5115  break;
5116  }
5117  }
5118  if( players_pending )
5119  {
5120  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
5121  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5122  {
5123  if( !player->IsLocalPlayer())
5124  {
5125  char num_seconds;
5126 
5127  num_seconds = 15;
5128 
5129  msg_desc.m_Data = &num_seconds;
5130  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( char );
5131  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_WAIT_N_SECONDS;
5132  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
5133  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
5134  m_server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
5135  }
5136  }
5137  m_server->SendData();
5138  }
5139 
5140 #endif
5141 
5142  // Add all pending players to the game
5143  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = next )
5144  {
5145  next = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true );
5146  if( player->m_flags.TestMask( PlayerInfo::mPENDING_PLAYER ))
5147  {
5148  NewPlayerInfo new_player;
5149 
5150  Dbg_Assert( player->IsObserving());
5151 
5152  num_new_players++;
5153 
5154  strcpy( new_player.Name, player->m_Name );
5155  new_player.ObjID = GetNextPlayerObjectId();
5156  new_player.Conn = player->m_Conn;
5157  new_player.Flags = PlayerInfo::mJUMPING_IN;
5158  new_player.Profile = player->m_Profile;
5159  new_player.Rating = player->m_Rating;
5160  new_player.VehicleControlType = player->m_VehicleControlType;
5161 
5162  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PushContext(Mem::Manager::sHandle().SkaterInfoHeap());
5163  *new_player.mpSkaterProfile = *player->mp_SkaterProfile;
5164  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PopContext();
5165 
5166  DestroyPlayer( player );
5167 
5168  DeferredNewPlayer( &new_player, ( num_new_players + 1 ) * vDEFERRED_JOIN_FRAMES );
5169 
5170  }
5171  }
5172 
5173  // Invalidate old positions. Player will be re-added to the world when we get a
5174  // sufficient number of object updates
5175  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh ); player; player = NextPlayerInfo( sh ))
5176  {
5177  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
5178  {
5179  continue;
5180  }
5181 
5182  player->m_Skater->RemoveFromCurrentWorld();
5183  player->m_Skater->Resync();
5184  }

5192 void Manager::StartNetworkLobby( void )

5207  }
5208  else
5209  {
5210  num_teams = skate_mod->GetGameMode()->NumTeams();
5211  }
5212

5214  m_gamemode_id = Script::GenerateCRC( "netlobby" );
5215  skate_mod->GetGameMode()->LoadGameType( m_gamemode_id );
5216  skate_mod->GetGameMode()->SetNumTeams( num_teams );
5217 
5218  m_game_over = false;
5219 
5220  // launches the game for this client
5221  // (should really wait until the clients are ready)
5222 
5223  //Mdl::ScriptRetry( NULL, NULL );
5224 
5225  ResetPlayers();
5226 
5227  Dbg_Printf( "Starting network lobby\n" );
5228 
5229  // Clear the king of the hill
5230  if(( player = GetKingOfTheHill()))
5231  {
5232  player->MarkAsKing( false );
5233  }
5234 
5235  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5236  {
5237  player->ClearCTFState();
5238  }
5239

5241 
5242  m_lobby_start_time = Tmr::GetTime();
5243

5248 /* */
5249 /******************************************************************/
5250 
5251 bool Manager::ShouldStopAtZero( void )
5252 {
5253  uint32 should_stop;
5254 
5255  if( ( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "netgoalattack" )) ||
5256  ( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "king" )) ||
5257  ( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "netking" )) ||
5258  ( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "netscorechallenge" )) ||
5259  ( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "scorechallenge" )))
5260  {
5261  return true;
5262  }
5263 
5264  if( InNetGame() == false )
5265  {
5266  return false;
5267  }
5268 
5269  if( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "netctf" ))
5270  {
5271  uint32 mode;
5272 
5273  mode = GetNetworkPreferences()->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("ctf_game_type"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
5274  if( mode != CRCD(0x938ab24b,"timed_ctf"))
5275  {
5276  return true;
5277  }
5278  }
5279 
5280  should_stop = GetNetworkPreferences()->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("stop_at_zero"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
5281  if( should_stop == CRCD(0xf81bc89b,"boolean_true"))
5282  {
5283  return true;
5284  }
5285 
5286  return false;
5287 }

5289 /******************************************************************/
5290 /* */
5291 /* */
5292 /******************************************************************/
5293 
5294 void Manager::StartNetworkGame( void )
5295 {
5296  PlayerInfo* player;
5297  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
5298  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
5299  int time_limit;
5300  Prefs::Preferences* pPreferences;
5301  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
5302 
5303  Dbg_MsgAssert( OnServer(),( "Server-only function called on client" ));
5304 
5305  pPreferences = NULL;
5306  if( InNetGame())
5307  {
5308  pPreferences = GetNetworkPreferences();
5309  }
5310  else
5311  {
5312  pPreferences = skate_mod->GetSplitScreenPreferences();
5313  }
5314 
5315 
5316 
5317  Net::Server* server;
5318  server = GetServer();
5319  Dbg_MsgAssert( server,( "Server has not been started\n" ));
5320 
5321  // Sorry boys, you didn't quite make it in
5322  free_all_pending_players();
5323 
5324  // set the game type for the server, from the network preferences
5325  m_gamemode_id = GetGameTypeFromPreferences();
5326  //skate_mod->GetGameMode()->LoadGameType( m_gamemode_id );
5327 
5328  // Mick: Moved this to after the setting of the game type, so we can check for horse mode in it
5329  // (used to explicitly set 1P and 2P start points in 2P split screen (not horse) game)
5330  RandomizeSkaterStartingPoints();
5331 
5332 
5333  if( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "horse" ))
5334  {
5335  time_limit = pPreferences->GetPreferenceValue( Script::GenerateCRC("horse_time_limit"), Script::GenerateCRC("time") );
5336  }
5337  else
5338  {
5339  time_limit = pPreferences->GetPreferenceValue( Script::GenerateCRC("time_limit"), Script::GenerateCRC("time") );
5340  }
5341 
5342  Dbg_Printf("Starting network game of type %s with time limit %d\n", Script::FindChecksumName(m_gamemode_id), time_limit);
5343  m_level_id = GetLevelFromPreferences();
5344 
5345  MsgGameInfo game_info_msg;
5346  game_info_msg.m_GameMode = m_gamemode_id;
5347  game_info_msg.m_FireballLevel = GetFireballLevelFromPreferences();
5348  Dbg_Printf( "***** FIREBALL LEVEL: %d\n", game_info_msg.m_FireballLevel );
5349  if( ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0xec200eaa,"netgoalattack")) ||
5350  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0x5d32129c,"king")) ||
5351  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0x6ef8fda0,"netking")) ||
5352  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0x1498240a,"netscorechallenge")) ||
5353  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0xf135ecb6,"scorechallenge")) ||
5354  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0x3d6d444f,"firefight")) ||
5355  ( m_gamemode_id == CRCD(0xbff33600,"netfirefight")))
5356  {
5357  game_info_msg.m_TimeLimit = 0;
5358  }
5359  else
5360  {
5361 
5362  if( m_gamemode_id == Script::GenerateCRC( "netctf" ))
5363  {
5364  uint32 mode;
5365 
5366  mode = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("ctf_game_type"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
5367  if( mode == CRCD(0x938ab24b,"timed_ctf"))
5368  {
5369  game_info_msg.m_TimeLimit = time_limit;
5370  }
5371  else
5372  {
5373  game_info_msg.m_TimeLimit = 0;
5374  }
5375  }
5376  else
5377  {
5378  game_info_msg.m_TimeLimit = time_limit;
5379  }
5380  }
5381 
5382  game_info_msg.m_StopAtZero = (char) ShouldStopAtZero();
5383  game_info_msg.m_TargetScore = pPreferences->GetPreferenceValue( Script::GenerateCRC("target_score"), Script::GenerateCRC("score") );
5384  Dbg_Printf( "Target score %d\n", (int)game_info_msg.m_TargetScore );
5385  game_info_msg.m_TeamMode = GetNumTeams();
5386 
5387  // Here, make sure we get a game id that does not match our last game id
5388  do
5389  {
5390  game_info_msg.m_GameId = 1 + (unsigned char) Mth::Rnd( 255 );
5391  } while( game_info_msg.m_GameId == m_last_end_of_run_game_id );
5392 
5393  game_info_msg.m_CrownSpawnPoint = m_crown_spawn_point;
5394  memcpy( game_info_msg.m_StartPoints, m_skater_starting_points, Mdl::Skate::vMAX_SKATERS * sizeof( int ));
5395 
5396  msg_desc.m_Data = &game_info_msg;
5397  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgGameInfo );
5398  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_GAME_INFO;
5399  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
5400  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
5401  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5402  {
5403  player->m_BestCombo = 0;
5404  player->ClearCTFState();
5405  player->m_flags.ClearMask( PlayerInfo::mRESTARTING );
5406  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
5407 
5408  // In splitscreen games, just send it to the first client
5409  if( InNetGame() == false )
5410  {
5411  break;
5412  }
5413  }
5414 
5415  // Clear the king of the hill
5416  if(( player = GetKingOfTheHill()))
5417  {
5418  player->MarkAsKing( false );
5419  }
5420  SetCurrentLeader( NULL );
5421  SetCurrentLeadingTeam( vNO_TEAM );
5422  ClearTriggerEventList();
5423  ResetPlayers();
5424  g_CheatsEnabled = false;
5425 
5426 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
5427  if( mpStatsMan->IsLoggedIn())
5428  {
5429  mpStatsMan->StartNewGame();
5430  }
5431 #endif
5432 }

5439 void Manager::ResetPlayers( void )
5440 {
5441  PlayerInfo* player;
5442  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
5443 
5444  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player;
5445  player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5446  {
5447  Mdl::Score* score;
5448  player->m_flags.ClearMask( PlayerInfo::mRUN_ENDED );
5449  if( player->m_Skater )
5450  {
5451  Obj::CSkaterScoreComponent* p_skater_score_component = GetSkaterScoreComponentFromObject(player->m_Skater);
5452  Dbg_Assert(p_skater_score_component);
5453  score = p_skater_score_component->GetScore();
5454 
5455  if( score )
5456  {
5457  score->Reset();
5458  }
5459  }
5460  }
5461 }

5660 bool Manager::ConnectToInternet( uint32 success_script, uint32 failure_script )
5661 {
5662 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
5663  Net::Manager * net_man = Net::Manager::Instance();
5664  Mlp::Manager * mlp_man = Mlp::Manager::Instance();
5665  bool was_online, is_online;
5666 
5667  m_connection_success_script = success_script;
5668  m_connection_failure_script = failure_script;
5669 
5670  Dbg_Printf( "Connecting to the internet\n" );
5671  was_online = net_man->IsOnline();
5672  if( was_online )
5673  {
5674  is_online = true;
5675  }
5676  else
5677  {
5678  m_last_modem_state = -1;
5679  is_online = net_man->ConnectToInternet();
5680  }
5681 
5682  if( is_online )
5683  {
5684  if( m_connection_success_script > 0 )
5685  {
5686  Script::RunScript( m_connection_success_script );
5687  }
5688  }
5689  else if(( net_man->GetConnectionType() == Net::vCONN_TYPE_MODEM ) ||
5690  ( net_man->GetConnectionType() == Net::vCONN_TYPE_PPPOE ))
5691  {
5692  mlp_man->AddLogicTask( *m_modem_state_task );
5693  }
5694 
5695  return is_online;
5696 #else
5697 #ifdef __PLAT_XBOX__
5698  mpAuthMan->UserLogon();
5699 #endif // __PLAT_XBOX__
5700 
5701  return false;
5702 #endif // __PLAT_NGPS__
5703 }
5704 
5705 /******************************************************************/
5706 /* */
5707 /* */
5708 /******************************************************************/
5709 
5710 void Manager::CancelConnectToInternet( void )
5711 {
5712 
5713  Net::Manager * net_man = Net::Manager::Instance();
5714  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
5715 
5716  switch( net_man->GetModemState())
5717  {
5718  case Net::vMODEM_STATE_DIALING:
5719  case Net::vMODEM_STATE_CONNECTED:
5720  gamenet_man->RemoveModemStateTask();
5721  gamenet_man->DisconnectFromInternet();
5722  break;
5723  case Net::vMODEM_STATE_ERROR:
5724 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
5725  if( net_man->GetModemError() == SNTC_ERR_NOMODEM )
5726  {
5727  Script::RunScript( gamenet_man->m_connection_failure_script );
5728  }
5729  else
5730  {
5731  gamenet_man->RemoveModemStateTask();
5732  gamenet_man->DisconnectFromInternet();
5733  break;
5734  }
5735 #endif // __PLAT_NGPS__
5736  gamenet_man->RemoveModemStateTask();
5737  break;;
5738  case Net::vMODEM_STATE_DISCONNECTED:
5739  Dbg_Printf( "Removing modem state task\n" );
5740  gamenet_man->RemoveModemStateTask();
5741  Script::RunScript( gamenet_man->m_connection_failure_script );
5742  break;
5743  case Net::vMODEM_STATE_LOGGED_IN:
5744  {
5745  net_man->SetModemState( Net::vMODEM_STATE_READY_TO_TRANSMIT );
5746  break;
5747  }
5748  default:
5749  break;
5750 
5751  }
5752 }

5759 void Manager::DisconnectFromInternet( uint32 callback_script )
5760 {
5761  Mlp::Manager * mlp_man = Mlp::Manager::Instance();
5762  Net::Manager * net_man = Net::Manager::Instance();
5763 
5764  Dbg_Assert( ( net_man->GetConnectionType() == Net::vCONN_TYPE_MODEM ) ||
5765  ( net_man->GetConnectionType() == Net::vCONN_TYPE_PPPOE ));
5766 
5767  m_last_modem_state = -1;
5768  if( callback_script != 0 )
5769  {
5770  m_connection_failure_script = callback_script;
5771  }
5772 
5773  mlp_man->AddLogicTask( *m_modem_state_task );
5774  SetServerListState( vSERVER_LIST_STATE_SHUTDOWN );
5775  net_man->DisconnectFromInternet();
5776 }

5778 /******************************************************************/
5779 /* */
5780 /* */
5781 /******************************************************************/
5782 
5783 void Manager::CreateNetPanelMessage( bool broadcast, uint32 message_checksum, char* string_parm_1,
5784  char* string_parm_2, Obj::CMovingObject* object, char* properties, bool important,
5785  int time )
5786 {
5787  if( broadcast )
5788  {
5789  PlayerInfo* player;
5790  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
5791  MsgPanelMessage msg;
5792  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
5793 
5794  msg.m_Parm1[0] = '\0';
5795  msg.m_Parm2[0] = '\0';
5796  msg.m_StringId = message_checksum;
5797  msg.m_Time = time;
5798  msg.m_PropsStructureCRC = (int) Script::GenerateCRC( properties );
5799  if( string_parm_1 )
5800  {
5801  strcpy( msg.m_Parm1, string_parm_1 );
5802  }
5803  if( string_parm_2 )
5804  {
5805  strcpy( msg.m_Parm2, string_parm_2 );
5806  }
5807 
5808  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
5809  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgPanelMessage );
5810  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_PANEL_MESSAGE;
5811  if( important )
5812  {
5813  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
5814  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
5815  }
5816 
5817  Dbg_Assert( m_server );
5818  for( player = FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player;
5819  player = NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
5820  {
5821  m_server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
5822  }
5823  }
5824  else
5825  {
5826  Script::CScriptStructure* pStructure = new Script::CScriptStructure;
5827  const char* text;
5828  char temp_msg[256];
5829  char final_msg[256];
5830  char* format_start;
5831 
5832  text = Script::GetLocalString( message_checksum );
5833  strcpy( temp_msg, text );
5834  if(( format_start = strstr( temp_msg, "%s0" )))
5835  {
5836  *format_start = '\0';
5837 
5838  strcpy( final_msg, temp_msg );
5839  Dbg_Assert( string_parm_1 ); // Need a parameter for this format string
5840  strcat( final_msg, string_parm_1 );
5841  format_start += 3; // skip the format tag
5842  strcat( final_msg, format_start );
5843 
5844  pStructure->AddComponent( Script::GenerateCRC( "Text" ), ESYMBOLTYPE_STRING, final_msg );
5845  }
5846  else
5847  {
5848  pStructure->AddComponent( Script::GenerateCRC( "Text" ), ESYMBOLTYPE_STRING, text );
5849  }
5850 
5851  pStructure->AddComponent( Script::GenerateCRC( "id" ), ESYMBOLTYPE_NAME, Script::GenerateCRC( "net_panel_msg" ));
5852  pStructure->AddInteger( Script::GenerateCRC( "msg_time" ), time );
5853  Script::RunScript( "create_net_panel_message", pStructure );
5854 
5855  delete pStructure;
5856  }
5857 }

5859 /******************************************************************/
5860 /* */
5861 /* */
5862 /******************************************************************/
5863 
5864 bool Manager::ShouldSendScoreUpdates( void )
5865 {
5866  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
5867 
5868  Game::CGameMode* pGameMode = skate_mod->GetGameMode();
5869 
5870  // We need to send score updates in goal attack
5871  if( ( pGameMode->ShouldAccumulateScore() == false ) &&
5872  ( pGameMode->ShouldTrackBestCombo() == false ) &&
5873  ( pGameMode->GetNameChecksum() != CRCD(0xbff33600,"netfirefight")) &&
5874  ( pGameMode->GetNameChecksum() != CRCD(0xec200eaa,"netgoalattack")) &&
5875  ( pGameMode->GetNameChecksum() != CRCD(0x6c5ff266,"netctf")))
5876  {
5877  return false;
5878  }
5879 
5880  if( pGameMode->EndConditionsMet() && ( pGameMode->GetNameChecksum() != CRCD(0xbff33600,"netfirefight")))
5881  {
5882  return false;
5883  }
5884 
5885  return true;
5886 }

5969 /* */
5970 /* */
5971 /******************************************************************/
5972 
5973 void Manager::AddSpawnedTriggerEvent( int node, int obj_id, uint32 script )
5974 {
5975  TriggerEvent* queued_script;
5976  Lst::Search< TriggerEvent > sh;
5977 
5978  // Check to make sure we don't queue duplicate scripts
5979  for( queued_script = sh.FirstItem( m_trigger_events ); queued_script;
5980  queued_script = sh.NextItem())
5981  {
5982  if( queued_script->m_Script == script )
5983  {
5984  return;
5985  }
5986  }
5987 
5988  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PushContext(Mem::Manager::sHandle().NetworkHeap());
5989 
5990  TriggerEvent* event = new TriggerEvent;
5991 
5992  event->m_Node = node;
5993  event->m_ObjID = obj_id;
5994  event->m_Script = script;
5995 
5996  m_trigger_events.AddToTail( event );
5997 
5998  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PopContext();
5999 }

6003 /* */

6005 
6006 void Manager::ClearTriggerEventList( void )
6007 {
6008  Lst::Search< TriggerEvent > sh;
6009  TriggerEvent* event, *next;
6010 
6011  for( event = sh.FirstItem( m_trigger_events ); event; event = next )
6012  {
6013  next = sh.NextItem();
6014  delete event;
6015  }
6016 }

6028 /******************************************************************/
6029 /* */
6030 /* */
6031 /******************************************************************/
6032 
6033 void Manager::SendChatMessage( char* message )
6034 {
6035 
6036  MsgChat msg;
6037  int size;
6038  PlayerInfo* player;
6039  Script::CStruct* p_params;
6040  char final_msg[256];
6041  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
6042 
6043  Dbg_Assert( message );
6044  Dbg_Assert( m_client[0] );
6045 
6046  // No point in printing/sending an empty message
6047  if( message[0] == '\0' )
6048  {
6049  return;
6050  }
6051 
6052  player = GetLocalPlayer();
6053  Dbg_Assert( player );
6054 
6055  strcpy( msg.m_Name, player->m_Name );
6056  strcpy( msg.m_ChatMsg, message );
6057  if( player->IsObserving() )
6058  {
6059  msg.m_ObjId = Mdl::Skate::vMAX_SKATERS; // Signifies "observer"
6060  }
6061  else
6062  {
6063  msg.m_ObjId = player->m_Skater->GetID();
6064  }
6065 
6066  size = sizeof( char ) + ( vMAX_PLAYER_NAME_LEN + 1 ) + strlen( message ) + 1;
6067 
6068  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
6069  msg_desc.m_Length = size;
6070  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_CHAT;
6071  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
6072  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
6073  m_client[0]->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
6074 
6075  p_params = new Script::CStruct;
6076  sprintf( final_msg, "%s : %s", player->m_Name, message );
6077  p_params->AddString( "text", final_msg );
6078  Script::RunScript("create_console_message", p_params );
6079  delete p_params;
6080 }

6122 /******************************************************************/
6123 /* */
6124 /* */
6125 /******************************************************************/
6126 
6127 void Manager::LaunchQueuedScripts( void )
6128 {
6129  TriggerEvent* queued_script, *next;
6130  Lst::Search< TriggerEvent > sh;
6131  Sfx::CSfxManager * pSfxManager = Sfx::CSfxManager::Instance();
6132  Mdl::Skate * mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
6133  Script::CScript* pScript;
6134 
6135  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PushContext(Mem::Manager::sHandle().BottomUpHeap());
6136 
6137  mod->SetLaunchingQueuedScripts();
6138  // Remember the original volume, then turn sound off so scripts don't make noise
6139  float orig_volume = pSfxManager->GetMainVolume();
6140  pSfxManager->SetMainVolume( 0.0f );
6141 
6142  Dbg_Printf( "********************* SPAWNING QUEUED SCRIPTS ******************\n" );
6143 
6144  Script::RunScript( "PreRunQueuedScripts" );
6145  for( queued_script = sh.FirstItem( m_trigger_events ); queued_script; queued_script = next )
6146  {
6147  Script::EScriptReturnVal ret_val;
6148 
6149  next = sh.NextItem();
6150 
6151  pScript = Script::SpawnScript( queued_script->m_Script, NULL, 0, NULL,
6152  queued_script->m_Node ); // K: The 0,NULL bit means no callback script specified
6153  #ifdef __NOPT_ASSERT__
6154  pScript->SetCommentString("Spawned from Manager::LaunchQueuedScripts");
6155  #endif
6156  pScript->mpObject = mod->GetObjectManager()->GetObjectByID( queued_script->m_ObjID );;
6157 
6158  // Now run script to completion
6159  do
6160  {
6161  ret_val = pScript->Update();
6162  // Script must not get blocked, otherwise it'll hang in this loop forever.
6163  Dbg_MsgAssert( ret_val!=Script::ESCRIPTRETURNVAL_BLOCKED,("\n%s\nScript got blocked when being run by RunScript.",pScript->GetScriptInfo()));
6164 
6165  } while( ret_val != Script::ESCRIPTRETURNVAL_FINISHED );
6166  Script::KillSpawnedScript(pScript);
6167  delete queued_script;
6168  }
6169 
6170  Script::RunScript( "PostRunQueuedScripts" );
6171 
6172  Dbg_Printf( "********************* FINISHED SPAWNING QUEUED SCRIPTS ******************\n" );
6173 
6174  // Back to normal volume
6175  pSfxManager->SetMainVolume( orig_volume );
6176  mod->ClearLaunchingQueuedScripts();
6177 
6178  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PopContext();
6179 }

6435 bool Manager::ScriptTookFlag(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
6436 {
6437  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
6438  PlayerInfo* player, *capture_player;
6439  Net::Server* server;
6440  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
6441  MsgFlagMsg msg;
6442  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
6443  int obj_id, team;
6444 
6445  pParams->GetInteger( "player", &obj_id );
6446  pParams->GetInteger( "flag_team", &team );
6447 
6448  capture_player = gamenet_man->GetPlayerByObjectID( obj_id );
6449  if( capture_player == NULL )
6450  {
6451  return true;
6452  }
6453 
6454  msg.m_ObjId = (char) obj_id;
6455  msg.m_Team = (char) team;
6456 
6457  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
6458  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgFlagMsg );
6459  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_TOOK_FLAG;
6460  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
6461  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
6462 
6463  server = gamenet_man->GetServer();
6464  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
6465  {
6466  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
6467  {
6468  capture_player->TookFlag( team );
6469  continue;
6470  }
6471  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
6472  }
6473 
6474  return true;
6475 }

6477 /******************************************************************/
6478 /* */
6479 /* */
6480 /******************************************************************/
6481 
6482 bool Manager::ScriptCapturedFlag(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
6483 {
6484  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
6485  PlayerInfo* player, *capture_player;
6486  Net::Server* server;
6487  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
6488  MsgFlagMsg msg;
6489  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
6490  int obj_id, team;
6491 
6492  pParams->GetInteger( "player", &obj_id );
6493  capture_player = gamenet_man->GetPlayerByObjectID( obj_id );
6494  if(( capture_player == NULL ) || ( capture_player->m_flags.TestMask( PlayerInfo::mRESTARTING )))
6495  {
6496  return true;
6497  }
6498 
6499  team = capture_player->HasWhichFlag();
6500  msg.m_ObjId = (char) obj_id;
6501  msg.m_Team = (char) team;
6502 
6503  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
6504  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgFlagMsg );
6505  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_CAPTURED_FLAG;
6506  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
6507  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
6508 
6509  server = gamenet_man->GetServer();
6510  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
6511  {
6512  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
6513  {
6514  Mdl::Score* score_obj;
6515 
6516  Obj::CSkaterScoreComponent* p_skater_score_component = GetSkaterScoreComponentFromObject(capture_player->m_Skater);
6517  Dbg_Assert(p_skater_score_component);
6518  score_obj = p_skater_score_component->GetScore();
6519 
6520  Dbg_Assert(score_obj);
6521  score_obj->SetTotalScore( score_obj->GetTotalScore() + 1 );
6522 
6523  capture_player->CapturedFlag( team );
6524  continue;
6525  }
6526  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
6527  }
6528 
6529  return true;
6530 }

6648 
6649 // @script | SpawnCrown | spawn the king of the hill crown
6650 bool Manager::ScriptSpawnCrown(Script::CStruct *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
6651 {
6652  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
6653  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
6654 
6655  // Spawn the king of the hill crown
6656  gamenet_man->m_crown = new Obj::CCrown;
6657 
6658  int i, spawn_pt;
6659 
6660  Script::CArray *pNodeArray=Script::GetArray("NodeArray");
6661 
6662  // if there is no node array, then there are no restart points
6663  if (!pNodeArray)
6664  {
6665  return false;
6666  }
6667 
6668  i = 0;
6669  spawn_pt = gamenet_man->m_crown_spawn_point;
6670 
6671  // collect a table of all crown nodes
6672  int max_crown_node = 0;
6673  Script::CStruct *pCrownNodeTab[vNUM_CROWN_SPAWN_POINTS];
6674  int crown_nodes[vNUM_CROWN_SPAWN_POINTS];
6675  while( i < (int)pNodeArray->GetSize() )
6676  {
6677  uint32 TypeChecksum;
6678  Script::CStruct *pNode=pNodeArray->GetStructure(i);
6679 
6680  TypeChecksum = 0;
6681  pNode->GetChecksum("Type",&TypeChecksum);
6682  if( TypeChecksum == 0xaf86421b ) // checksum of "Crown"
6683  {
6684  Dbg_MsgAssert( max_crown_node < vNUM_CROWN_SPAWN_POINTS, ( "Too many crown spawn points" ));
6685  crown_nodes[max_crown_node] = i;
6686  pCrownNodeTab[max_crown_node++] = pNode;
6687  }
6688  i++;
6689  }
6690  Dbg_MsgAssert(max_crown_node, ("no crown nodes found"));
6691 
6692  // there may be fewer crown points than the one we want, so
6693  // truncate the request number if so
6694  spawn_pt = spawn_pt % max_crown_node;
6695 
6696  // now set up crown point in world
6697  Mth::Vector pos;
6698  SkateScript::GetPosition( pCrownNodeTab[spawn_pt], &pos );
6699 
6700  gamenet_man->m_crown->InitCrown( skate_mod->GetObjectManager(), pCrownNodeTab[spawn_pt] );
6701 
6702  PlayerInfo* king;
6703  //gamenet_man->m_crown->AddToWorld( viewer_mod->GetCurrentWorld(), &pos );
6704 
6705  // We may have a king "queued" up (i.e. we joined a KOTH game in progress.
6706  // If so, coronate the king straight away
6707  king = gamenet_man->GetKingOfTheHill();
6708  if( king )
6709  {
6710  gamenet_man->m_crown->PlaceOnKing( king->m_Skater );
6711  }
6712 
6713  return true;
6714 }

6734 // @script | StartNetworkGame |
6735 bool Manager::ScriptStartNetworkGame(Script::CStruct *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
6736 {
6737  Mlp::Manager * mlp_man = Mlp::Manager::Instance();
6738  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
6739  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
6740 
6741  if( gamenet_man->m_start_network_game_task->InList())
6742  {
6743  return true;
6744  }
6745  if( gamenet_man->m_change_level_task->InList())
6746  {
6747  return true;
6748  }
6749 
6750  gamenet_man->m_game_pending = true;
6751  if( gamenet_man->InNetGame())
6752  {
6753  if( gamenet_man->GetGameTypeFromPreferences() == Script::GenerateCRC( "netgoalattack" ))
6754  {
6755  s_time_to_start_game = Tmr::GetTime() + vTIME_BEFORE_STARTING_GOALATTACK;
6756 
6757  }
6758  else
6759  {
6760  s_time_to_start_game = Tmr::GetTime() + vTIME_BEFORE_STARTING_NETGAME;
6761  }
6762  }
6763  else
6764  {
6765  s_time_to_start_game = Tmr::GetTime();
6766  }
6767 
6768  mlp_man->AddLogicTask( *gamenet_man->m_start_network_game_task );
6769 
6770  if( gamenet_man->InNetGame())
6771  {
6772  if( gamenet_man->GetHostMode() == vHOST_MODE_AUTO_SERVE )
6773  {
6774  gamenet_man->CreateNetPanelMessage( true, Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_auto_starting_game"),
6775  gamenet_man->GetGameModeName(), NULL, NULL, "netstatusprops", true,
6776  Tmr::Seconds( 3 ));
6777  }
6778  else
6779  {
6780  gamenet_man->CreateNetPanelMessage( true, Script::GenerateCRC("net_message_starting_game"),
6781  gamenet_man->GetGameModeName(), NULL, NULL, "netstatusprops", true,
6782  Tmr::Seconds( 3 ));
6783  }
6784 
6785  if( skate_mod->GetGameMode()->IsTeamGame())
6786  {
6787  Net::Server* server;
6788  PlayerInfo* player;
6789  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
6790  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
6791 
6792  server = gamenet_man->GetServer();
6793  Dbg_Assert( server );
6794 
6795  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_KILL_TEAM_FLAGS;
6796  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
6797  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
6798  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
6799  {
6800  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
6801  }
6802  }
6803  }
6804 
6805  // Compile the list of selected goals to send to all clients at the start of goal attack games
6806  if( gamenet_man->InNetGame() && ( gamenet_man->GetGameTypeFromPreferences() == Script::GenerateCRC( "netgoalattack" )))
6807  {
6808  int i, num_goals;
6809  Game::CGoalManager* pGoalManager;
6810  Game::CGoal* pGoal;
6811  Net::MsgMax msg;
6812  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
6813  uint32 goal_id;
6814  char* data;
6815  Net::Server* server;
6816  PlayerInfo* player;
6817  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
6818 
6819  pGoalManager = Game::GetGoalManager();
6820  server = gamenet_man->GetServer();
6821  Dbg_Assert( server );
6822 
6823  data = msg.m_Data;
6824  *data++ = 1; // This indicates that they should bring up the goal summary dialog
6825  num_goals = pGoalManager->GetNumGoals();
6826  Dbg_Printf( "*** Num Goals: %d\n" );
6827  for( i = 0; i < num_goals; i++ )
6828  {
6829  pGoal = pGoalManager->GetGoalByIndex( i );
6830  Dbg_Assert( pGoal );
6831  if( pGoal->IsSelected())
6832  {
6833  pGoal->UnBeatGoal();
6834  goal_id = pGoal->GetGoalId();
6835  Dbg_Printf( "*** Goals %d selected, id 0x%x\n", i, goal_id );
6836  memcpy( data, &goal_id, sizeof( uint32 ));
6837  data += sizeof( uint32 );
6838  }
6839  }
6840 
6841  // zero-terminate the list of goals
6842  goal_id = 0;
6843  memcpy( data, &goal_id, sizeof( uint32 ));
6844  data += sizeof( uint32 );
6845 
6846  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
6847  msg_desc.m_Length = (int) ( data - msg.m_Data );
6848  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_SELECT_GOALS;
6849  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
6850  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
6851  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
6852  {
6853  // No need to send to server
6854  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
6855  {
6856  continue;
6857  }
6858  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &msg_desc );
6859  }
6860 
6861  }
6862 
6863  return true;
6864 }

7060 
7061 bool Manager::ScriptSetNumTeams(Script::CStruct *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7062 {
7063  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7064  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
7065  PlayerInfo* team_player, *player;
7066  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > team_sh, sh;
7067  MsgChangeTeam msg;
7068  MsgByteInfo num_teams_msg;
7069  Net::MsgDesc team_msg_desc;
7070  int num_teams = 0;
7071  Net::Server* server;
7072 
7073  pParams->GetInteger( NONAME, &num_teams );
7074 
7075  if( !gamenet_man->OnServer())
7076  {
7077  Net::Client* client;
7078  MsgByteInfo team_msg;
7079  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
7080 
7081  client = gamenet_man->GetClient( 0 );
7082 
7083  team_msg.m_Data = num_teams;
7084  Dbg_Printf( "Telling server to create %d teams\n", num_teams );
7085 
7086  msg_desc.m_Data = &team_msg;
7087  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgByteInfo );
7088  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_FCFS_SET_NUM_TEAMS;
7089  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7090  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7091  client->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
7092  return true;
7093  }
7094 
7095  if( ( num_teams > 0 ) &&
7096  ( !skate_mod->GetGameMode()->IsTeamGame()))
7097  {
7098  skate_mod->GetGameMode()->SetNumTeams( num_teams );
7099  if( skate_mod->GetLocalSkater())
7100  {
7101  Script::RunScript( "PrepareSkaterForMove", NULL, skate_mod->GetLocalSkater());
7102  skate_mod->move_to_restart_point( skate_mod->GetLocalSkater());
7103  }
7104  }
7105  else
7106  {
7107  skate_mod->GetGameMode()->SetNumTeams( num_teams );
7108  }
7109 
7110  server = gamenet_man->GetServer();
7111  if( server == NULL )
7112  {
7113  return true;
7114  }
7115 
7116  num_teams_msg.m_Data = num_teams;
7117 
7118  team_msg_desc.m_Data = &num_teams_msg;
7119  team_msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgByteInfo );
7120  team_msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_SET_NUM_TEAMS;
7121  team_msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7122  team_msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7123 
7124  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
7125  {
7126  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
7127  {
7128  continue;
7129  }
7130  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &team_msg_desc );
7131  }
7132 
7133  team_msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
7134  team_msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgChangeTeam );
7135  team_msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_TEAM_CHANGE;
7136  team_msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7137  team_msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7138  for( team_player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( team_sh ); team_player; team_player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( team_sh ))
7139  {
7140  if( team_player->m_Team >= num_teams )
7141  {
7142  msg.m_Team = (unsigned char) vTEAM_RED;
7143  msg.m_ObjID = (unsigned char) team_player->m_Skater->GetID();
7144 
7145  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
7146  {
7147  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
7148  {
7149  continue;
7150  }
7151  server->EnqueueMessage( player->GetConnHandle(), &team_msg_desc );
7152  }
7153  team_player->m_Team = vTEAM_RED;
7154  }
7155  }
7156 
7157  return true;
7158 }

7160 /******************************************************************/
7161 /* */
7162 /* */
7163 /******************************************************************/
7164 
7165 bool Manager::ScriptJoinTeam(Script::CStruct *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7166 {
7167  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7168  PlayerInfo* player;
7169  MsgChangeTeam msg;
7170  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
7171  Net::Client* client;
7172  uint32 team_checksum;
7173  int team;
7174  static Tmr::Time s_last_join_time = 0;
7175 
7176  player = gamenet_man->GetLocalPlayer();
7177  if( ( player == NULL ) ||
7178  ( player->m_Skater == NULL ))
7179  {
7180  return false;
7181  }
7182 
7183  pParams->GetChecksum( NONAME, &team_checksum );
7184  if( team_checksum == Script::GenerateCRC( "blue" ))
7185  {
7186  team = vTEAM_BLUE;
7187  }
7188  else if( team_checksum == Script::GenerateCRC( "red" ))
7189  {
7190  team = vTEAM_RED;
7191  }
7192  else if( team_checksum == Script::GenerateCRC( "green" ))
7193  {
7194  team = vTEAM_GREEN;
7195  }
7196  else
7197  {
7198  team = vTEAM_YELLOW;
7199  }
7200 
7201  msg.m_Team = (unsigned char) team;
7202  msg.m_ObjID = (unsigned char) player->m_Skater->GetID();
7203  client = gamenet_man->GetClient( 0 );
7204  if(( Tmr::GetTime() - s_last_join_time ) < 150 )
7205  {
7206  return true;
7207  }
7208  s_last_join_time = Tmr::GetTime();
7209 
7210  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
7211  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgChangeTeam );
7212  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_REQUEST_CHANGE_TEAM;
7213  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7214  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7215  client->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
7216 
7217  return true;
7218 }

7287 
7288 bool Manager::ScriptIsAutoServing(Script::CStruct *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7289 {
7290  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7291 
7292  if( gamenet_man->InNetGame() == false )
7293  {
7294  return false;
7295  }
7296 
7297  if( gamenet_man->OnServer() == false )
7298  {
7299  return false;
7300 
7301  }

7471 /* */
7472 /******************************************************************/
7473 
7474 bool Manager::ScriptCreatePlayerOptions(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7475 {
7476  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7477  Script::CScriptStructure* pStructure;
7478  PlayerInfo* player;
7479  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
7480  int index;
7481  const char* name;
7482 
7483  index = 0;
7484  name = NULL;
7485  pParams->GetInteger( Script::GenerateCRC("index"), &index );
7486  pParams->GetString( Script::GenerateCRC("name"), &name );
7487 
7488  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
7489  {
7490  if( index == 0 )
7491  {
7492  if( stricmp( player->m_Name, name ) == 0 )
7493  {
7494  player->m_flags.SetMask( PlayerInfo::mMARKED_PLAYER );
7495 
7496  pStructure = new Script::CScriptStructure;
7497 
7498 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
7499  if( gamenet_man->InInternetMode())
7500  {
7501  if( ( player->m_Profile ) &&
7502  ( gamenet_man->mpBuddyMan->IsLoggedIn()))
7503  {
7504  pStructure->AddInteger( "profile", player->m_Profile );
7505  pStructure->AddString( "nick", player->m_Name );
7506 
7507  if( gamenet_man->mpBuddyMan->IsAlreadyMyBuddy( player->m_Profile ))
7508  {
7509  pStructure->AddChecksum( NONAME, Script::GenerateCRC( "allow_remove_homie" ));
7510  }
7511  else
7512  {
7513  pStructure->AddChecksum( NONAME, Script::GenerateCRC( "allow_add_homie" ));
7514  }
7515  }
7516  }
7517 #endif
7518  pStructure->AddComponent( Script::GenerateCRC( "name" ), ESYMBOLTYPE_STRING, name );
7519 
7520  Script::RunScript( "create_player_options_dialog", pStructure );
7521 
7522  delete pStructure;
7523  }
7524  break;
7525  }
7526 
7527  index--;
7528  }
7529 
7530  return true;
7531 }

7533 /******************************************************************/

7535 /* */
7536 /******************************************************************/
7537 #ifdef __PLAT_NGPS__
7538 bool Manager::ScriptFillPlayerListMenu( Script::CStruct* pParams, Script::CScript* pScript )
7539 {
7540  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7541  PlayerInfo* player;
7542  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
7543  Script::CStruct* p_item_params, *p_unfocus_params;
7544  Script::CArray* p_colors;
7545  int i;
7546 
7547  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PushContext(Mem::Manager::sHandle().FrontEndHeap());
7548 
7549  i = 0;
7550  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
7551  {
7552  if( player->IsLocalPlayer())
7553  {
7554  i++;
7555  continue;
7556  }
7557 
7558  p_colors = new Script::CArray;
7559  p_colors->SetSizeAndType( 4, ESYMBOLTYPE_INTEGER );

7562  ( gamenet_man->mpBuddyMan->IsLoggedIn()))

7567  p_colors->SetInteger( 1, 128 );
7568  p_colors->SetInteger( 2, 0 );
7569  p_colors->SetInteger( 3, 128 );
7570  }
7571  else
7572  {
7573  p_colors->SetInteger( 0, 0 );
7574  p_colors->SetInteger( 1, 128 );
7575  p_colors->SetInteger( 2, 0 );
7576  p_colors->SetInteger( 3, 128 );
7577  }
7578  }
7579  else
7580  {
7581  p_colors->SetInteger( 0, 128 );
7582  p_colors->SetInteger( 1, 128 );
7583  p_colors->SetInteger( 2, 128 );
7584  p_colors->SetInteger( 3, 128 );
7585  }

7589  p_item_params->AddChecksum( "centered", CRCD(0x2a434d05,"centered") );

7591  p_item_params->AddChecksum( "pad_choose_script",Script::GenerateCRC("choose_selected_player"));
7592 
7593  p_unfocus_params = new Script::CStruct;
7594  p_unfocus_params->AddArray( "rgba", p_colors );
7595  p_item_params->AddArray( "rgba", p_colors );
7596  p_item_params->AddStructure( "unfocus_params", p_unfocus_params );
7597 
7598  // create the parameters that are passed to the X script
7599  Script::CStruct *p_script_params= new Script::CStruct;
7600  p_script_params->AddInteger( "index", i );
7601  p_script_params->AddString( "name", player->m_Name );
7602  p_item_params->AddStructure("pad_choose_params",p_script_params);
7603 
7604  Script::RunScript("theme_menu_add_item",p_item_params);
7605 
7606  delete p_item_params;
7607  delete p_script_params;
7608  delete p_unfocus_params;
7609  delete p_colors;
7610  i++;
7611  }
7612 
7613  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PopContext();
7614 
7615  return true;
7616 }

7680 /******************************************************************/
7681 /* */
7682 /* */
7683 /******************************************************************/
7684 
7685 bool Manager::ScriptKickPlayer(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7686 {
7687  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7688  PlayerInfo* player;
7689  Lst::Search< PlayerInfo > sh;
7690  int i;
7691 
7692  i = 0;
7693  for( player = gamenet_man->FirstPlayerInfo( sh, true ); player; player = gamenet_man->NextPlayerInfo( sh, true ))
7694  {
7695  if( player->m_flags.TestMask( PlayerInfo::mMARKED_PLAYER ))
7696  {
7697  if( gamenet_man->OnServer())
7698  {
7699  Obj::CSkater* quitting_skater;
7700  bool observing;
7701 
7702  quitting_skater = player->m_Skater;
7703  observing = player->IsObserving();
7704  gamenet_man->DropPlayer( player, vREASON_KICKED );
7705  if( !observing )
7706  {
7707  Mdl::Skate * skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
7708  skate_mod->remove_skater( quitting_skater );
7709  }
7710  }
7711  else
7712  {
7713  Net::Client* client;
7714  MsgRemovePlayerRequest msg;
7715  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
7716 
7717  client = gamenet_man->GetClient( 0 );
7718  Dbg_Assert( client );
7719 
7720  msg.m_Ban = 0;
7721  msg.m_Index = i;
7722  strcpy( msg.m_Name, player->m_Name );
7723 
7724  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
7725  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgRemovePlayerRequest );
7726  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_FCFS_BAN_PLAYER;
7727  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7728  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7729  client->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
7730 
7731  }
7732  break;
7733  }
7734  i++;
7735  }
7736 
7737  return true;
7738 }

7806 
7807 bool Manager::ScriptFCFSRequestStartGame(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7808 {
7809  MsgStartGameRequest msg;
7810  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
7811  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7812  Net::Client* client;
7813  Prefs::Preferences* pPreferences;
7814 
7815  pPreferences = gamenet_man->GetNetworkPreferences();
7816  msg.m_SkillLevel = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("skill_level"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7817  msg.m_FireballLevel = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("fireball_difficulty"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7818  msg.m_GameMode = gamenet_man->GetGameTypeFromPreferences();
7819  msg.m_TimeLimit = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("time_limit"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7820  msg.m_TargetScore = 0;
7821  msg.m_TargetScore = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("target_score"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7822  Dbg_Printf( "************ SENDING TARGET SCORE OF %08x\n", msg.m_TargetScore );
7823  msg.m_PlayerCollision = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("player_collision"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7824  msg.m_FriendlyFire = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("friendly_fire"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7825  msg.m_StopAtZero = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("stop_at_zero"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7826  msg.m_CTFType = pPreferences->GetPreferenceChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC("ctf_game_type"), Script::GenerateCRC("checksum") );
7827 
7828  // FCFS functions should only happen on clients
7829  Dbg_Assert( !gamenet_man->OnServer());
7830 
7831  client = gamenet_man->GetClient( 0 );
7832  Dbg_Assert( client );
7833 
7834  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
7835  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgStartGameRequest );
7836  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_FCFS_START_GAME;
7837  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7838  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7839  client->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
7840 
7841  gamenet_man->m_game_pending = true;
7842  return true;
7843 }

7846 /* */
7847 /* */
7848 /******************************************************************/
7849 
7850 bool Manager::ScriptFCFSRequestChangeLevel(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
7851 {
7852  uint32 level;
7853  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
7854  MsgIntInfo msg;
7855  Net::MsgDesc msg_desc;
7856  Net::Client* client;
7857 
7858  // Need to limit this option. Make sure a second request doesn't go out while waiting for the first
7859  // to complete
7860 
7861  // FCFS functions should only happen on clients
7862  Dbg_Assert( !gamenet_man->OnServer());
7863 
7864  level = 0;
7865  pParams->GetChecksum( Script::GenerateCRC( "level" ), &level );
7866  msg.m_Data = (int) level;
7867 
7868  client = gamenet_man->GetClient( 0 );
7869  Dbg_Assert( client );
7870 
7871  if( level == CRCD(0xb664035d,"Load_Sk5Ed_gameplay"))
7872  {
7873  client->StreamMessageToServer( MSG_ID_LEVEL_DATA, Ed::CParkManager::COMPRESSED_MAP_SIZE,
7874  Ed::CParkManager::sInstance()->GetCompressedMapBuffer(), "level data", vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS );
7875 
7876  client->StreamMessageToServer( MSG_ID_RAIL_DATA, Obj::GetRailEditor()->GetCompressedRailsBufferSize(),
7877  Obj::GetRailEditor()->GetCompressedRailsBuffer(), "rail data", vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS );
7878 
7879  }
7880 
7881  msg_desc.m_Data = &msg;
7882  msg_desc.m_Length = sizeof( MsgIntInfo );
7883  msg_desc.m_Id = MSG_ID_FCFS_CHANGE_LEVEL;
7884  msg_desc.m_Queue = Net::QUEUE_SEQUENCED;
7885  msg_desc.m_GroupId = vSEQ_GROUP_PLAYER_MSGS;
7886  client->EnqueueMessageToServer( &msg_desc );
7887 
7888  return true;
7889 }

8033 bool Manager::ScriptResetProSetFlags(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)

8080 bool Manager::ScriptEnterSurveyorMode(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
8081 {
8082  Inp::Manager * inp_manager = Inp::Manager::Instance();
8083  Mlp::Manager* mlp_man = Mlp::Manager::Instance();
8084  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
8085  PlayerInfo* local_player;
8086 
8087  local_player = gamenet_man->GetLocalPlayer();
8088  if( local_player->IsObserving() || local_player->IsSurveying())
8089  {
8090  return false;
8091  }
8092 
8093  Dbg_Printf( "Entering surveyor mode\n" );
8094  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PushContext(Mem::Manager::sHandle().NetworkHeap());
8095 
8096  local_player->m_observer_logic_task =
8097  new Tsk::Task< PlayerInfo > ( PlayerInfo::s_observer_logic_code, *local_player );
8098  mlp_man->AddLogicTask( *local_player->m_observer_logic_task );
8099  gamenet_man->m_observer_input_handler = new Inp::Handler< Manager > ( 0, s_observer_input_logic_code, *gamenet_man,
8100  Tsk::BaseTask::Node::vHANDLER_PRIORITY_OBSERVER_INPUT_LOGIC );
8101  inp_manager->AddHandler( *gamenet_man->m_observer_input_handler );
8102 
8103  local_player->m_flags.SetMask( PlayerInfo::mSURVEYING );
8104 
8105  Mem::Manager::sHandle().PopContext();
8106 
8107  return true;
8108 }

8115 bool Manager::ScriptExitSurveyorMode(Script::CScriptStructure *pParams, Script::CScript *pScript)
8116 {
8117  Manager * gamenet_man = Manager::Instance();
8118  PlayerInfo* local_player;
8119 
8120  local_player = gamenet_man->GetLocalPlayer();
8121  if( !local_player )
8122  {
8123  return false;
8124  }
8125 
8126  Dbg_Assert( !( local_player->IsObserving()));
8127 
8128  if( local_player->IsSurveying() == false )
8129  {
8130  return true;
8131  }
8132 
8133  Dbg_Printf( "Exiting surveyor mode\n" );
8134  gamenet_man->ObservePlayer( local_player );
8135  delete local_player->m_observer_logic_task;
8136  local_player->m_observer_logic_task = NULL;
8137  delete gamenet_man->m_observer_input_handler;
8138  gamenet_man->m_observer_input_handler = NULL;
8139 
8140  local_player->m_flags.ClearMask( PlayerInfo::mSURVEYING );
8141 
8142  return true;
8143 }

8149 
8150 void Manager::SetReadyToPlay(bool ready_to_play)
8151 {
8152  if (ready_to_play == m_ready_to_play) return;
8153 
8154  m_ready_to_play = ready_to_play;
8155 
8156  // Dan: moved from the beginning of CSkater::DoServerLogic(). I'm sort of just moving a hack, instead of fixing it...
8157 
8158  // keep the skater from skating around before he it ready
8159  if (!Mdl::Skate::Instance()->GetGameMode()->IsTrue( "is_frontend" ))
8160  {
8161  if (m_ready_to_play)
8162  {
8163  Mdl::Skate* skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
8164  uint32 NumSkaters = skate_mod->GetNumSkaters();
8165  for (uint32 i = 0; i < NumSkaters; ++i)
8166  {
8167  Obj::CSkater *pSkater = skate_mod->GetSkater(i);
8168  if (pSkater)
8169  {
8170  pSkater->UnPause();
8171  }
8172  }
8173  }
8174  else
8175  {
8176  Mdl::Skate* skate_mod = Mdl::Skate::Instance();
8177  uint32 NumSkaters = skate_mod->GetNumSkaters();
8178  for (uint32 i = 0; i < NumSkaters; ++i)
8179  {
8180  Obj::CSkater *pSkater = skate_mod->GetSkater(i);
8181  if (pSkater)
8182  {
8183  pSkater->Pause();
8184  }
8185  }
8186  }
8187  }
8188 }
